   "source": [
    "# 8. QAM正交幅度调制基础\n",
    "\n",
    "**QAM Basics - Beginner**\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "本notebook是通信基础系列的第八课，我们将学习正交幅度调制（Quadrature Amplitude Modulation, QAM）。QAM是现代数字通信系统中最重要的调制方式之一，广泛应用于WiFi、5G、卫星通信和数字广播电视等领域。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. 学习目标\n",
    "\n",
    "通过本notebook，您将：\n",
    "\n",
    "- **理解QAM的正交幅度调制原理**：掌握如何使用两个正交载波同时传输两路独立数据\n",
    "- **掌握I/Q调制的概念**：理解同相分量(I)和正交分量(Q)如何构成复数信号\n",
    "- **理解星座图距离与误码率的关系**：掌握星座点间欧氏距离如何影响抗噪声性能\n",
    "- **了解高阶QAM（16/64/256-QAM）**：认识调制阶数与频谱效率、抗噪声性能的权衡"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. 概念讲解\n",
    "\n",
    "### 2.1 QAM原理：两路正交载波合成\n",
    "\n",
    "QAM的核心思想是利用两个正交（即相位相差90度）的载波同时传输两路独立信息：\n",
    "\n",
    "- **同相载波 (In-Phase, I)**：$cos(2\\pi f_c t)$\n",
    "- **正交载波 (Quadrature, Q)**：$sin(2\\pi f_c t)$\n",
    "\n",
    "**QAM调制信号表达式**：\n",
    "\n",
    "$$s(t) = I(t) \\cdot \\cos(2\\pi f_c t) - Q(t) \\cdot \\sin(2\\pi f_c t)$$\n",
    "\n",
    "这里 I(t) 和 Q(t) 是两路独立的基带信号，它们可以是多电平的模拟信号。\n",
    "\n",
    "**为什么叫\"正交\"调制？**\n",
    "\n",
    "由于 $cos(2\\pi f_c t)$ 和 $sin(2\\pi f_c t)$ 在一个符号周期内满足正交性（即它们的乘积积分为零），因此这两路信号可以同时传输而互不干扰，在相同带宽内实现了频谱效率翻倍。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 2.2 I/Q表示：复数信号视角\n",
    "\n",
    "从复数的角度看，QAM信号可以表示为复数信号的实部：\n",
    "\n",
    "$$s(t) = \\text{Re}\\{(I(t) + jQ(t)) \\cdot e^{j2\\pi f_c t}\\} = \\text{Re}\\{x(t) \\cdot e^{j2\\pi f_c t}\\}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "其中：\n",
    "- $x(t) = I(t) + jQ(t)$ 称为**复包络**或**基带信号**\n",
    "- I路是复包络的实部\n",
    "- Q路是复包络的虚部\n",
    "\n",
    "**复平面上的QAM星座图**：\n",
    "\n",
    "在复平面上，每个QAM符号对应一个点：\n",
    "- **实轴（I轴）**：同相分量\n",
    "- **虚轴（Q轴）**：正交分量\n",
    "\n",
    "例如，16-QAM的每个星座点坐标为 (I, Q)，每个点代表一个4比特符号。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 2.3 16-QAM星座图详解\n",
    "\n",
    "16-QAM是最常用的QAM调制方式之一，它在平面上形成4×4=16个星座点。\n",
    "\n",
    "**16-QAM的星座点分布**：\n",
    "\n",
    "```\n",
    "        Q\n",
    "        ↑\n",
    "     3  ●  ●  ●  ●\n",
    "     1  ●  ●  ●  ●\n",
    "    -1  ●  ●  ●  ●\n",
    "    -3  ●  ●  ●  ●\n",
    "        └─────────→ I\n",
    "          -3  -1   1   3\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "**16-QAM的特点**：\n",
    "\n",
    "| 参数 | 值 |\n",
    "|------|-----|\n",
    "| 星座点数 | 16 |\n",
    "| 每符号比特数 | 4 |\n",
    "| I路电平数 | 4 |\n",
    "| Q路电平数 | 4 |\n",
    "| 最小欧氏距离 | 2/3（归一化后）|"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 2.4 高阶QAM的频谱效率与抗噪声性能权衡\n",
    "\n",
    "QAM的阶数M决定了每符号携带的比特数和抗噪声性能。\n",
    "\n",
    "**常见QAM调制方式对比**：\n",
    "\n",
    "| 调制方式 | 星座点数M | 每符号比特数 | 频谱效率(bit/s/Hz) | 相对抗噪声能力 |\n",
    "|----------|----------|------------|-------------------|---------------|\n",
    "| 4-QAM (QPSK) | 4 | 2 | 2 | 最强 |\n",
    "| 16-QAM | 16 | 4 | 4 | 强 |\n",
    "| 64-QAM | 64 | 6 | 6 | 中等 |\n",
    "| 256-QAM | 256 | 8 | 8 | 较弱 |\n",
    "\n",
    "**权衡关系**：\n",
    "\n",
    "- **更高阶QAM**：频谱效率更高（每符号传更多比特），但星座点更密集，最小欧氏距离减小，抗噪声能力下降\n",
    "- **更低阶QAM**：频谱效率较低，但星座点间距更大，抗噪声能力更强\n",
    "\n",
    "这就是通信系统中\"带宽\"与\"可靠性\"之间的经典权衡。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 3. Python演示\n",
    "\n",
    "下面我们使用Python来演示QAM调制的原理和特性。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "%matplotlib inline\n",
    "\n",
    "# 设置中文字体支持\n",
    "plt.rcParams['font.sans-serif'] = ['SimHei', 'DejaVu Sans']\n",
    "plt.rcParams['axes.unicode_minus'] = False\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"QAM调制演示环境已准备就绪\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 3.1 16-QAM星座图绘制"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def create_qam16_constellation():\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    创建16-QAM星座图，使用格雷码映射\n",
    "    \n",
    "    16-QAM有16个星座点，每个点对应4个比特\n",
    "    星座点坐标为 (-3,-3), (-3,-1), (-1,-3), ... 等\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    # 定义I路和Q路的电平值（归一化）\n",
    "    levels = np.array([-3, -1, 1, 3]) / 3.0  # 归一化到[-1, 1]范围\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 格雷码映射表（4比特）\n",
    "    # 格雷码的特点：相邻码只有1比特不同\n",
    "    gray_code = [\n",
    "        '0000', '0001', '0011', '0010',  # 第1行\n",
    "        '0100', '0101', '0111', '0110',  # 第2行\n",
    "        '1100', '1101', '1111', '1110',  # 第3行\n",
    "        '1010', '1011', '1001', '1000'   # 第4行\n",
    "    ]\n",
    "    \n",
    "    qam16 = []\n",
    "    bit_labels = []\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 生成所有16个星座点\n",
    "    for i, level_i in enumerate(levels):\n",
    "        for j, level_q in enumerate(levels):\n",
    "            idx = i * 4 + j\n",
    "            qam16.append(level_i + 1j * level_q)\n",
    "            bit_labels.append(gray_code[idx])\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return np.array(qam16), bit_labels\n",
    "\n",
    "# 创建16-QAM星座点\n",
    "qam16_constellation, bit_labels = create_qam16_constellation()\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"16-QAM星座点数量: {len(qam16_constellation)}\")\n",
    "print(f\"每符号携带比特数: {int(np.log2(len(qam16_constellation)))} bit\")\n",
    "print(f\"I路范围: [{qam16_constellation.real.min():.2f}, {qam16_constellation.real.max():.2f}]\")\n",
    "print(f\"Q路范围: [{qam16_constellation.imag.min():.2f}, {qam16_constellation.imag.max():.2f}]\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 绘制16-QAM星座图\n",
    "fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 10))\n",
    "\n",
    "# 绘制星座点\n",
    "ax.scatter(qam16_constellation.real, qam16_constellation.imag, \n",
    "           c='blue', s=150, marker='o', edgecolors='black', linewidths=1.5)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 为每个星座点添加比特标签\n",
    "for point, label in zip(qam16_constellation, bit_labels):\n",
    "    ax.annotate(label, (point.real, point.imag), \n",
    "                textcoords=\"offset points\", xytext=(8, 8), \n",
    "                ha='left', fontsize=9, color='red')\n",
    "\n",
    "# 绘制坐标轴\n",
    "ax.axhline(y=0, color='k', linewidth=1)\n",
    "ax.axvline(x=0, color='k', linewidth=1)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 设置图形属性\n",
    "ax.set_xlabel('同相分量 (I)', fontsize=14)\n",
    "ax.set_ylabel('正交分量 (Q)', fontsize=14)\n",
    "ax.set_title('16-QAM星座图（带格雷码映射）', fontsize=16)\n",
    "ax.grid(True, alpha=0.3, linestyle='--')\n",
    "ax.set_xlim(-1.5, 1.5)\n",
    "ax.set_ylim(-1.5, 1.5)\n",
    "ax.set_aspect('equal')\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "plt.show()\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"\\n观察要点：\")\n",
    "print(\"  1. 16-QAM形成4×4=16个星座点\")\n",
    "print(\"  2. 每个点对应4个比特（如'0000', '0001'等）\")\n",
    "print(\"  3. 水平或垂直相邻的星座点只相差1比特（格雷码特性）\")\n",
    "print(\"  4. 这种设计使得噪声引起的误判通常只导致1比特错误\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 3.2 QAM调制解调完整流程演示"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def qam16_modulation(bits):\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    16-QAM调制：将4比特映射为复数星座点\n",
    "    \n",
    "    参数：bits - 输入比特序列（长度必须是4的倍数）\n",
    "    返回：复数QAM符号序列\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    # 格雷码到星座点的映射\n",
    "    gray_to_constellation = {\n",
    "        '0000': -3-3j, '0001': -3-1j, '0011': -3+1j, '0010': -3+3j,\n",
    "        '0100': -1-3j, '0101': -1-1j, '0111': -1+1j, '0110': -1+3j,\n",
    "        '1100':  1-3j, '1101':  1-1j, '1111':  1+1j, '1110':  1+3j,\n",
    "        '1010':  3-3j, '1011':  3-1j, '1001':  3+1j, '1000':  3+3j\n",
    "    }\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 归一化处理\n",
    "    normalized_mapping = {k: v/3 for k, v in gray_to_constellation.items()}\n",
    "    \n",
    "    symbols = []\n",
    "    for i in range(0, len(bits), 4):\n",
    "        bit_group = ''.join(map(str, bits[i:i+4]))\n",
    "        if bit_group in normalized_mapping:\n",
    "            symbols.append(normalized_mapping[bit_group])\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return np.array(symbols)\n",
    "\n",
    "def qam16_demodulation(symbols):\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    16-QAM解调：将复数星座点映射回比特\n",
    "    \n",
    "    参数：symbols - 接收到的复数符号序列\n",
    "    返回：解调后的比特序列\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    # 归一化后的标准16-QAM星座点\n",
    "    constellation = np.array([\n",
    "        -3-3j, -3-1j, -3+1j, -3+3j,\n",
    "        -1-3j, -1-1j, -1+1j, -1+3j,\n",
    "         1-3j,  1-1j,  1+1j,  1+3j,\n",
    "         3-3j,  3-1j,  3+1j,  3+3j\n",
    "    ]) / 3.0\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 格雷码映射表\n",
    "    gray_code = [\n",
    "        '0000', '0001', '0011', '0010',\n",
    "        '0100', '0101', '0111', '0110',\n",
    "        '1100', '1101', '1111', '1110',\n",
    "        '1010', '1011', '1001', '1000'\n",
    "    ]\n",
    "    \n",
    "    bits = []\n",
    "    for symbol in symbols:\n",
    "        # 找到最近的星座点（最小欧氏距离判决）\n",
    "        distances = np.abs(symbol - constellation)\n",
    "        nearest_idx = np.argmin(distances)\n",
    "        # 转换为比特\n",
    "        bits.extend([int(b) for b in gray_code[nearest_idx]])\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return np.array(bits)\n",
    "\n",
    "def add_awgn_noise(signal, snr_db):\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    添加高斯白噪声（AWGN）\n",
    "    \n",
    "    参数：\n",
    "        signal - 输入信号（复数）\n",
    "        snr_db - 信噪比（dB）\n",
    "    返回：加噪后的信号\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    # 计算信号功率\n",
    "    signal_power = np.mean(np.abs(signal)**2)\n",
    "    # 根据SNR计算噪声功率\n",
    "    snr_linear = 10**(snr_db/10)\n",
    "    noise_power = signal_power / snr_linear\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 生成复高斯噪声\n",
    "    noise = np.sqrt(noise_power/2) * (np.random.randn(len(signal)) + 1j * np.random.randn(len(signal)))\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return signal + noise\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"QAM调制解调函数已定义\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 演示完整的QAM调制解调流程\n",
    "np.random.seed(42)  # 设置随机种子以便重复实验\n",
    "\n",
    "# 1. 生成随机比特序列\n",
    "num_symbols = 20  # 发送20个QAM符号\n",
    "bits = np.random.randint(0, 2, num_symbols * 4)  # 每个符号4比特\n",
    "print(f\"发送比特数: {len(bits)}\")\n",
    "print(f\"发送比特示例: {bits[:20]}...\")  # 显示前20个比特\n",
    "\n",
    "# 2. QAM调制\n",
    "tx_symbols = qam16_modulation(bits)\n",
    "print(f\"\\n调制后符号数: {len(tx_symbols)}\")\n",
    "print(f\"发送符号示例: {tx_symbols[:5]}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# 3. 通过AWGN信道\n",
    "snr_db = 15  # 信噪比15dB\n",
    "rx_symbols = add_awgn_noise(tx_symbols, snr_db)\n",
    "print(f\"\\n信道SNR: {snr_db} dB\")\n",
    "print(f\"接收符号示例: {rx_symbols[:5]}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# 4. QAM解调\n",
    "rx_bits = qam16_demodulation(rx_symbols)\n",
    "print(f\"\\n解调后比特数: {len(rx_bits)}\")\n",
    "print(f\"接收比特示例: {rx_bits[:20]}...\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# 5. 计算误码\n",
    "errors = np.sum(bits != rx_bits)\n",
    "ber = errors / len(bits)\n",
    "print(f\"\\n误码数: {errors}\")\n",
    "print(f"误码率: {ber:.4f}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 可视化调制解调星座图\n",
    "fig, axes = plt.subplots(1, 2, figsize=(16, 7))\n",
    "\n",
    "# 发送端星座图\n",
    "axes[0].scatter(tx_symbols.real, tx_symbols.imag, \n",
    "               c='blue', s=100, alpha=0.7, edgecolors='black', linewidths=1)\n",
    "# 叠加标准星座点（淡灰色）\n",
    "axes[0].scatter(qam16_constellation.real, qam16_constellation.imag, \n",
